# Text Summarizer App

This Streamlit app uses a pre-trained BART model from Hugging Face to generate concise summaries of user-provided text.

## Features

- Interactive text input area
- Adjustable summarization settings:
  - Maximum summary length
  - Number of beams for beam search decoding
- Clear visual feedback for summarization settings

## Running the App

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone <your_github_repo_url>
```

### 2. Install Dependencies

```bash
cd text-summarizer-app
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3. Run the App

```bash
streamlit run app.py
```

## Deployment

This app is deployed on Streamlit Sharing: [Streamlit Sharing URL](https://share.streamlit.io/your_username/text-summarizer-app/) (replace with your Streamlit Sharing URL)

